Metadata.Title: Technical Difficulties
Metadata.Description: Your job is simple this time 47.Infiltrate the villa's undergorund mainframe and eliminate key technicians.While you are doing this make sure to also destroy the 4 main servers.Even though the owners can manually reset the system, the absence of these technicians will ensure the key assets can never be fully recovered which will seriously hemorage rival operations.As for your weapon, one of our undercover operatives on the island has left a sharpened seashell near the escape plane.Good luck
